      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02-mku009.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんが「美味しいわ」って自信満々に言って\n優ちゃんとすみれちゃんが困った顔で笑ってたよ",
      "startTime": 93.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
