      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02-mku010.m4a",
      "text": "レタス味のグミが好きなら、ネギ味のグミがあったら\n瑠依ちゃんは食べてくれるかな？",
      "startTime": 105.7666666667,
