      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02-mku011.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんには京都弁と、京都でよく使う言葉を\n教えてもらったの",
